Hi just a small guid for powerleveling a ca with dd's or cl's as secondary's.

This guid is for world 4-2, 2 or 3 nodes and every run free steel.

It is less moral intensive and less boring then 3-2A at the cost of very few buckets.
==Guide==
You have to max mordernise the firepower for the CA (have it kai'd) and have your dd's at least at lvl 25~30 (also kai'd) and mordernised. It is recommended to stop after node H, so it will cost you almost no buckets. You can however continue for rare drops at the bos node but you will have most likely 2~3 taihai'd ships.(and you can even turn on the weekly [[Quest#Bw1|Bw1]]  sorty to boss quest, if you wish to continue). 

If you don't have at least one strong 20.3 cm gun for the CA change the BBV gun to 15cm red main gun.


